LUMINOUS GLASS DISTRIBUTORS OF FLORIDA, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
AEROTEK, INC., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-0568 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 25, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 17, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
